OL,3,CCampaign for Gigi heads to Downing
OL,4,CStreet
OL,6,FKate Roughley, who was the nursery's
OL,7,Fdeputy manager at the time of baby
OL,8,FGenevieve's death, was found guilty of
OL,9,Fmanslaughter and jailed for 14 years
OL,10,Fin May 2024.
OL,12,FLater today, Genevieve's parents -
OL,13,FKatie and John - will hand deliver a
OL,14,Fletter to Number 10 as they call for
OL,15,Flaw changes to help prevent similar
OL,16,Ftragedies in the future.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
