OL,3,CCampaign for Gigi heads to Downing
OL,4,CStreet
OL,6,F"On 9th May 2022, we left our 9 month
OL,7,Fold daughter in the care of her
OL,8,Fnursery; an act undertaken by tens of
OL,9,Fthousands of parents across the
OL,10,Fcountry every day. The next time we
OL,11,Fsaw her, she was dead, killed by the
OL,12,Fnursery worker that was supposed to
OL,13,Fcare for her.
OL,15,F"Gigi had been put to sleep in a
OL,16,Fmanifestly dangerous manner. At trial,
OL,17,Fthose responsible sought to rely on
OL,18,Fthe absence of clear statutory
OL,19,Frequirements for safe sleep in
OL,20,Fnurseries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
