OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F392A1768814422
OL,3,CCampaign for Gigi heads to Downing
OL,4,CStreet
OL,6,F"The nursery Gigi attended had been
OL,7,Frated Good by Ofsted. In common with
OL,8,Fmost parents, we relied on that
OL,9,Frating. We did not know that the
OL,10,FOfsted inspection process was not fit
OL,11,Ffor purpose.
OL,13,F"We did not know that, prior to Gigi's
OL,14,Fdeath, Ofsted had received complaints
OL,15,Ffrom staff and parents about the
OL,16,Fwelfare of children at the nursery,
OL,17,Fbut despite this, no intervention took
OL,18,Fplace. Whistleblowing did not save
OL,19,FGigi.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
