CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F392A1768814422
OL,3,CCampaign for Gigi heads to Downing
OL,4,CStreet
OL,6,F"Gigi's death was recorded on CCTV.
OL,7,FThis footage demonstrated conclusively
OL,8,Fthat Gigi and other children had been
OL,9,Fmistreated. The CCTV footage was
OL,10,Favailable to Ofsted. However, it did
OL,11,Fnot view it as part of its inspection
OL,12,Fprocess. Had the footage been reviewed
OL,13,Fby Ofsted we have no doubt Gigi would
OL,14,Fbe alive. Furthermore, without this
OL,15,FCCTV, Gigi would not have got justice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
