PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F392A1768814422
OL,3,CCampaign for Gigi heads to Downing
OL,4,CStreet
OL,6,F"This Government has made it a
OL,7,Fpriority to increase the provision of
OL,8,Fnursery places. That is a laudable
OL,9,Faim. However, in the absence of an
OL,10,Fequally strong commitment to improve
OL,11,Fsafety in nurseries, the result of
OL,12,Fthat policy is to risk placing more
OL,13,Fchildren into unsafe environments.
OL,14,FKeeping children safe must be priority
OL,15,Fof any government.
OL,17,F"That is why we are campaigning for
OL,19,F"1. Clear statutory requirements as to
OL,20,Fsafe sleep in nurseries
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
