PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F392A1768814422
OL,3,CCampaign for Gigi heads to Downing
OL,4,CStreet
OL,6,F"2. A strengthened and robust Ofsted
OL,7,Finspection process including the
OL,8,Froutine use of unannounced inspections
OL,10,F"3. National safe sleep training for
OL,11,Fall Ofsted inspectors and nursery staff
OL,13,F"4. Mandatory CCTV in nurseries
OL,15,F"We know that the Department of
OL,16,FEducation has met with experts from
OL,17,FThe Lullaby Trust to discuss changes
OL,18,Fto the EYFS, however those changes
OL,19,Fhave not yet been implemented. This
OL,20,Fputs children's lives at risk.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
