OL,3,CCampaign for Gigi heads to Downing
OL,4,CStreet
OL,6,F"Gigi deserved to live her life and to
OL,7,Fflourish. That was so cruelly taken
OL,8,Faway from her. This Government must
OL,9,Fact now to prevent this from ever
OL,10,Fhappening again."
OL,12,FAfter delivering their letter, Katie
OL,13,Fand John will host an MP drop-in to
OL,14,Fbuild cross-party support for the
OL,15,Fcampaign, which is expected to be
OL,16,Fattended by the recently appointed
OL,17,FEarly Years Minister, Olivia Bailey MP.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
