OL,6,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester, Andy
OL,7,FBurnham, will also be there. His
OL,8,Foffice says the Greater Manchester
OL,9,FCombined Authority (GMCA) supports
OL,10,FCampaign for Gigi and is developing a
OL,11,F"safety in setting" action plan.
OL,13,FThe work is intended to support early
OL,14,Fyears providers in the city region,
OL,15,Fstrengthen safeguarding, and build the
OL,16,Fevidence base for the national reforms
OL,17,Fbeing sought through the campaign.
