OL,6,FThe government says it is reviewing
OL,7,Fcurrent arrangements and developing
OL,8,Fclearer guidance, including around
OL,9,Fsafe sleep, while considering whether
OL,10,Ffurther national changes are needed.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the Minister for Early
OL,12,FEducation, Olivia Bailey MP, said:
OL,14,F"Gigi's death was a devastating
OL,15,Ftragedy that should never have
OL,16,Fhappened, and my thoughts are with her
OL,17,Fparents, John and Katie.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
