OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F392A1768814422
OL,3,CCampaign for Gigi heads to Downing
OL,4,CStreet
OL,6,F"We are moving forward with new
OL,7,Fguidance on CCTV and digital devices
OL,8,Fthrough an expert panel, working with
OL,9,FThe Lullaby Trust to make safer sleep
OL,10,Frequirements clearer, and have
OL,11,Frecently strengthened safeguarding
OL,12,Frequirements in the Early Years
OL,13,FFoundation Stage while reviewing what
OL,14,Ffurther changes are needed, with every
OL,15,Fconcern raised through the Campaign
OL,16,Ffor Gigi carefully considered."
